President Donald J. Trump has announced his intention to appoint Stephen A. Feinberg to a key position in his Administration. Feinberg, the co-founder, Executive Chairman, and Co-Chief Executive Officer of Cerberus Capital Management, will become a Member and Chair of the President's Intelligence Advisory Board. With over 30 years of experience in conducting organizational assessments, operational improvements, and complex reforms, Feinberg brings a wealth of knowledge to his new role. He is a graduate of Princeton University and hails from Spring Valley, New York.